{"tid":356402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係成人從零開始學結他，","createTime":"2017-08-12T05:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T00:21:49.000Z","uid":103499,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01f065bea781cd569b3ca493d14c09963040d3f8","tid":356402,"uid":103499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:02:31.000Z","msg":"會唔會好難學，音感好差，唱歌五音不全，拍子感差，但對聽歌有興趣，亦想自己演奏下，初學有咩注意地方，點樣自學？"},{"pid":"6b038600b19814274187745a911bd21b0d0f0abe","tid":356402,"uid":45580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:05:40.000Z","msg":"我都想學"},{"pid":"59d611fa851c026d6d2a37ff5143a743738d1baa","tid":356402,"uid":119937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"lm. 報過一季工聯班都未學識"},{"pid":"a5432b4e5546b79ce87bcedda5cce44008ad7322","tid":356402,"uid":76159,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm. 報過一季工聯班都未學識</blockquote><br />\n工聯班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成功率好低"},{"pid":"468b2351d7b5be3ee68fb02dcd89a41a7cb47bb3","tid":356402,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會好難學，音感好差，唱歌五音不全，拍子感差，但對聽歌有興趣，亦想自己演奏下，初學有咩注意地方，點樣自學？</blockquote><br />\n唔要彈得勁睇youtube堆教學都夠"},{"pid":"2499059856604e7024f1dadae7a5bc5517ae526e","tid":356402,"uid":51108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:08:36.000Z","msg":"24歲果陣買咗支結他，叫朋友教<br />\n兩個月後放棄咗<br />\n真係好難<br />\n<br />\n利申識彈琴，識睇譜"},{"pid":"19e492f51c26210350b1b96cbc442c6164f53a74","tid":356402,"uid":103499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:11:32.000Z","msg":"我5線譜都唔識睇"},{"pid":"f07c3c26e20f9c1939975ef05f7d9bf04b707358","tid":356402,"uid":103499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>24歲果陣買咗支結他，叫朋友教<br />\n兩個月後放棄咗<br />\n真係好難<br />\n<br />\n利申識彈琴，識睇譜</blockq