174f3727ca","tid":356402,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"最緊要狂練<br />\n彈下自己鍾意嘅歌較容易有成功感"},{"pid":"d25f8ce2fc9c2dba4868c1baf2a525f0aafe3778","tid":356402,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"我28歲先學，早多兩年有跟人學過，但連個C chord 都㩒唔到。兩年後，再買咗把結他，自己的起心肝自學，<br />\n經過無數次後終於㩒到C chord.....<br />\n所以，只要唔放棄！幾歲、有無天份都會學到！加油！"},{"pid":"1b17f6f6ddeab6944e02b50e04f4e6db3e9ab6e6","tid":356402,"uid":103499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多巴打請分享心得，我細細個冇機會學，依家想為自己做番補番。"},{"pid":"cf9e5d8f636ed1c9b699fb515e40691d7206cfc4","tid":356402,"uid":51108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T06:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>24歲果陣買咗支結他，叫朋友教<br />\n兩個月後放棄咗<br />\n真係好難<br />\n<br />\n利申識彈琴，識睇譜</blockquote><br />\n係咪真正好難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係。同埋人大咗真係冇咁好定力同你坐係到粒幾兩粒鐘咁練結他"},{"pid":"819f750f5180f2d96eabab2942763951b42e265c","tid":356402,"uid":9997,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:04:32.000Z","msg":"有個好敗家嘅建議去迫你學，就係買支貴少少嘅結他"},{"pid":"42c4e85a0cf972f4ee121886cde1a0b2ed611124","tid":356402,"uid":58192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:07:38.000Z","msg":"20歲開始學，23歲先識流暢轉chord同少少finger style"},{"pid":"fffab772f91bcc7071e34375c06a7ed6c984f795","tid":356402,"uid":33768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:47:32.000Z","msg":"想問guitar pro有咩用?<br />\n我將右手guitar拆線轉左手有冇咩要留意<br />\n利申:新手"},{"pid":"8e4753fd1dc96b2ffd46b40c6d6090dab25c7e15","tid":356402,"uid":50123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問guitar pro有咩用?<br />\n我將右手guitar拆線轉左手有冇咩要留意<br />\n利申:新手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGuitar pro, 係一個軟件，寫譜用，你可以down左人地嘅譜播放，你跟住彈去練習。有band譜你仲可以mute左某種樂器聲，例如你mute左結他聲，咁你就可以更清楚知道彈得好唔好，同埋練習時冇咁悶<br />\n<br />\n有專for左手嘅結他賣"},{"pid":"2499fa0217281665448e4b8d9e462777f72ed36a","tid":356402,"uid":36403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"eca730fc97c1363f543234cc9451a4e763540074","tid":356402,"uid":35501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:28:04.000Z","msg":"有得揀都唔好自學<br />\n唔係唔得，不過彈錯無人執，唔明無人問，學得好慢"},{"pid":"d7cb8a6f31cc33e660bd5e54c4da28d8f0dd981f","tid":356402,"uid":44171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"巴打我都係自學撚, 大家努力由零開始, 最緊要有恆心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d8f32af06d13cbbb38ed18a406b95dad8d8760","tid":356402,"uid":73583,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"手指太短玩唔到 好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9077067e6bc9cc2abafe93a77ce1eb002da60e2c","tid":356402,"uid":50123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>手指太短玩唔到 好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔關事，你睇下YouTube d 5、6 歲"},{"pid":"600da884819291d9c21cec2df7dd0404d781d2b5","tid":356402,"uid":38815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:35:11.000Z","msg":"一黎買左枝PRS private stock<br />\n<br />\n玩左半個禮拜就放棄"},{"pid":"92219e38c71dabb7145a9808b8b234e78fe95c52","tid":356402,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:12:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一黎買左枝PRS private stock<br />\n<br />\n玩左半個禮拜就放棄</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c8e921edaf0623048cbc5415a49282390263d7","tid":356402,"uid":13885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:15:51.000Z","msg":"23歲先學 學左幾個月進度都幾好 <br />\n有心唔怕遲 如果天份唔係太差的話"},{"pid":"c5b54eb96e47bbea20c455b39b2ca65d05bd6d79","tid":356402,"uid":13885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:17:55.000Z","msg":"個人認為買支岩自己手既結他好緊要<br />\n寧願貴少少都唔買渣流結他"},{"pid":"8badd6343e6c6a0934a105c46a4774ef5c648c42","tid":356402,"uid":13885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>23歲先學 學左幾個月進度都幾好 <br />\n有心唔怕遲 如果天份唔係太差的話</blockquote><br />\n轉bar chord已經順 睇住譜自彈自唱已經無問題 學左半年到"},{"pid":"bd64a31a33c9f6194f2b94f887f0e4ad8986787d","tid":356402,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一黎買左枝PRS private stock<br />\n<br />\n玩左半個禮拜就放棄</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打400水同你收左佢可以? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db8d1e23bd11126bc56c76ce408671c8ab70022","tid":356402,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:22:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7abcca926886e71f012b0700f9e8253a788f4327","tid":356402,"uid":45328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:22:54.000Z","msg":"21歲開始自學木結他，0樂理底，都係靠上小學雞結他網同睇youtube，初初學按chord隻手真係好辛苦，一黎指頭痛，二黎d動作好唔自然，好快會好攰。但果陣因爲好想學識自彈自唱，頂硬上，不過好無系統咁學/練。大約半年已經可以勉強掃chord彈完一首歌，到而家基本上都可以彈得好自然。但由於好多野都係死記硬背，所以我都唔敢講自己真係識「彈」結他，但見到識嘅chord我就彈得出囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n而家自彈自唱基本上都smooth，但真係強烈建議跟老師學，一對一"},{"pid":"97cb04561139ed7cd84fa516e04e67f065744d04","tid":356402,"uid":40550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:26:50.000Z","msg":"我都係睇小學雞結他網<br />\n佢教得比較清晰啲<br />\n<br />\n至於一對一需唔需要就睇經濟能力<br />\n有能力當然一對一最好<br />\n無老師都可以上到手<br />\n只係比較容易放棄同埋慢好多咁解<br />\n<br />\n利申22個陣學"},{"pid":"9b2dfbc83488190f048e5c9c37f38e709fae9ba8","tid":356402,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十七歲開始學 三個月識彈普通chord 轉得順 第六個月開始識埋bar chord轉得順 之後e家玩緊finger style識彈幾首歌 吉他認真唔難 睇下你克唔克服到第一階段......手指超痛</blockquote><br />\n你後生就咁講<br />\n我28歲啱啱先學左半年<br />\n可能我地捱得痛<br />\n雖然有少少辛苦但問題不大(但要keep住彈，唔係啲皮薄番再彈又會痛)<br />\n我反而覺得個拍子最難搞<br />\n<br />\n我係覺得老左學得慢啲"},{"pid":"e2ce3706a6d82091b003372686b2adcd76f347ca","tid":356402,"uid":34023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我28歲先學，早多兩年有跟人學過，但連個C chord 都㩒唔到。兩年後，再買咗把結他，自己的起心肝自學，<br />\n經過無數次後終於㩒到C chord.....<br />\n所以，只要唔放棄！幾歲、有無天份都會學到！加油！</blockquote><br />\n哈哈<br />\n我都係買左支好少少嘅結他先的起心肝學"},{"pid":"d32bb10662649087d37d5726a332fa2d584df162","tid":356402,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十七歲開始學 三個月識彈普通chord 轉得順 第六個月開始識埋bar chord轉得順 之後e家玩緊finger style識彈幾首歌 吉他認真唔難 睇下你克唔克服到第一階段......手指超痛</blockquote><br />\n你後生就咁講<br />\n我28歲啱啱先學左半年<br />\n可能我地捱得痛<br />\n雖然有少少辛苦但問題不大(但要keep住彈，唔係啲皮薄番再彈又會痛)<br />\n我反而覺得個拍子最難搞<br />\n<br />\n我係覺得老左學得慢啲</blockquote><br />\n同埋換左線之後好彈好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"c8ffc16510bce7853d8c8305f10534deecd17323","tid":356402,"uid":128993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:32:34.000Z","msg":"其實樂器只係一個方式<br />\n最重要係你嘅音樂水平<br />\n姐係如果你音樂水平本身唔高，你學結他之餘其實仲要花好多時間係浸音樂水平<br />\n調返轉玩開音樂嘅，學其他樂器都會快啲pick up<br />\n所以你心理準備要好多時間去學"},{"pid":"bbbedd172d863117184b2a5b79a5ea02acc6d06a","tid":356402,"uid":58484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80159f11275bff0b5d57700491f7ff9ec618eb0d","tid":356402,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>十七歲開始學 三個月識彈普通chord 轉得順 第六個月開始識埋bar chord轉得順 之後e家玩緊finger style識彈幾首歌 吉他認真唔難 睇下你克唔克服到第一階段......手指超痛</blockquote><br />\n你後生就咁講<br />\n我28歲啱啱先學左半年<br />\n可能我地捱得痛<br />\n雖然有少少辛苦但問題不大(但要keep住彈，唔係啲皮薄番再彈又會痛)<br />\n我反而覺得個拍子最難搞<br />\n<br />\n我係覺得老左學得慢啲</blockquote><br />\n同埋換左線之後好彈好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</blockquote><br />\n換線只係賴地硬(除非你原廠係粗線啦),你bar唔到extra light都係bar 唔到"},{"pid":"096bbb484731baf034ca62f20b449036f50df0b3","tid":356402,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"我都想學<br />\n<br />\n而家21<br />\n對音樂0認知<br />\n<br />\n初入門買支木結先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16823cb77057732fbec703085488ec9f1b6d280f","tid":356402,"uid":120951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想學<br />\n<br />\n而家21<br />\n對音樂0認知<br />\n<br />\n初入門買支木結先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新手買支一兩千蚊Yamaha 玩住先<br />\n我一開始都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a1970cf2b001bef7e536ad3caf4f9ccb33d8de","tid":356402,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>十七歲開始學 三個月識彈普通chord 轉得順 第六個月開始識埋bar chord轉得順 之後e家玩緊finger style識彈幾首歌 吉他認真唔難 睇下你克唔克服到第一階段......手指超痛</blockquote><br />\n你後生就咁講<br />\n我28歲啱啱先學左半年<br />\n可能我地捱得痛<br />\n雖然有少少辛苦但問題不大(但要keep住彈，唔係啲皮薄番再彈又會痛)<br />\n我反而覺得個拍子最難搞<br />\n<br />\n我係覺得老左學得慢啲</blockquote><br />\n同埋換左線之後好彈好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</blockquote><br />\n換線只係賴地硬(除非你原廠係粗線啦),你bar唔到extra light都係bar 唔到</blockquote><br />\n原來果啲線玩左幾個線生晒銹<br />\n可能心理作用唔敢大力禁"},{"pid":"adde3c92f450e15c4a223e07d497ffb1c473b817","tid":356402,"uid":50123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>十七歲開始學 三個月識彈普通chord 轉得順 第六個月開始識埋bar chord轉得順 之後e家玩緊finger style識彈幾首歌 吉他認真唔難 睇下你克唔克服到第一階段......手指超痛</blockquote><br />\n你後生就咁講<br />\n我28歲啱啱先學左半年<br />\n可能我地捱得痛<br />\n雖然有少少辛苦但問題不大(但要keep住彈，唔係啲皮薄番再彈又會痛)<br />\n我反而覺得個拍子最難搞<br />\n<br />\n我係覺得老左學得慢啲</blockquote><br />\n同埋換左線之後好彈好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</blockquote><br />\n換線只係賴地硬(除非你原廠係粗線啦),你bar唔到extra light都係bar 唔到</blockquote><br />\n原來果啲線玩左幾個線生晒銹<br />\n可能心理作用唔敢大力禁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n線用耐左係要換，因應每個人保養，使用程度，手汗都唔同，舊左嘅線張力會細左，聲會鈍左，手感差左，仲會易斷d"},{"pid":"278522c750c88d12ae39426db070b58ea11d7118","tid":356402,"uid":88250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:16:17.000Z","msg":"26歲膽粗粗入通X買新手set自學學左幾年<br />\n而架彈到 Slash Godfather<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經好滿足<br />\n<br />\n肯練習其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97ad8f9850e944cc3531c58b4e5e3da1673d670","tid":356402,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>26歲膽粗粗入通X買新手set自學學左幾年<br />\n而架彈到 Slash Godfather<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經好滿足<br />\n<br />\n肯練習其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔難系列 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我真係覺結他真係好難開頭, 要頂得到痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9768cd877c49011a13dcbe67cb48f4fdb267b329","tid":356402,"uid":18953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"bar 左好耐都bar 唔到 放棄左"},{"pid":"5efad6fafea1761bd542515d98164ebb44dbf2a4","tid":356402,"uid":32645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"18歲學左幾個月木結就放低左<br />\n尼兩年真心想學好結他所以買左個幾貴既電結焗到自己keep住學落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5bb58e8028967d84c8c92804b8567374cfc541","tid":356402,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:29:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會好難學，音感好差，唱歌五音不全，拍子感差，但對聽歌有興趣，亦想自己演奏下，初學有咩注意地方，點樣自學？</blockquote><br />\n對聽歌有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f25978fa67b8bc21287e32fad181d8b2b2a317","tid":356402,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bar 左好耐都bar 唔到 放棄左</blockquote><br />\n我之前都bar唔到，練練下，無啦啦有日訓醒就bar到<br />\n個下成功感好大，玩結他係好開心，唔好放棄啦"},{"pid":"d71f7db2fe35f406c5837793f352c6272931c281","tid":356402,"uid":115504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會好難學，音感好差，唱歌五音不全，拍子感差，但對聽歌有興趣，亦想自己演奏下，初學有咩注意地方，點樣自學？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有個fd同你情況一樣<br />\n兩個禮拜已經玩轉流行曲<br />\n係數拍子都仲練緊"},{"pid":"cc34efbfdc6700b78a54b7b69f3ff410b5e1d91c","tid":356402,"uid":37416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"有無人從零開始學bass"},{"pid":"0bb76aa5461393826fe156eb3f3caf9e18ded3bc","tid":356402,"uid":88250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>26歲膽粗粗入通X買新手set自學學左幾年<br />\n而架彈到 Slash Godfather<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經好滿足<br />\n<br />\n肯練習其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔難系列 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我真係覺結他真係好難開頭, 要頂得到痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痛就抖下，練下其他野<br />\n練bend線開始都係痛到pk, 唔放棄每次有dd進步就夠<br />\n結他係難學，要捱到熟左個fretboard先好玩，但有心絕對係人人都學到<br />\n<br />\n只要不斷去練一d未學好既野，自然就會有進步。最pk係學識新野掛住自high"},{"pid":"292f0a6dadc5ac33de6cc075517b8bb8c7031aa7","tid":356402,"uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:27:38.000Z","msg":"我係高登搵過老師<br />\n一對一教學極都彈唔到個chord<br />\n冇天份真係冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f731f9facfa6b9b5b6195196cff1dc296a1f4865","tid":356402,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係高登搵過老師<br />\n一對一教學極都彈唔到個chord<br />\n冇天份真係冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好話你懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a52a1043a06150075a208702c898bbff1e17d8","tid":356402,"uid":88829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:33:56.000Z","msg":"17歲 先學<br />\n雖則 好快 識 哂基本chord<br />\n但後尾 玩fingerstyle 就 一直停滯 不前"},{"pid":"ffce580b486d072c0f17ba7b290cf4d26db26208","tid":356402,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十七歲開始學 三個月識彈普通chord 轉得順 第六個月開始識埋bar chord轉得順 之後e家玩緊finger style識彈幾首歌 吉他認真唔難 睇下你克唔克服到第一階段......手指超痛</blockquote><br />\n痴藥水膠布有冇幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b034d678cc658488f21a39d530cc13fb7e5b2a","tid":356402,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十七歲開始學 三個月識彈普通chord 轉得順 第六個月開始識埋bar chord轉得順 之後e家玩緊finger style識彈幾首歌 吉他認真唔難 睇下你克唔克服到第一階段......手指超痛</blockquote><br />\n痴藥水膠布有冇幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開頭痛咪停一停先, 過兩日指尖啲皮厚咗就冇事"},{"pid":"fb6858ce76dcd76a82385f8a02e08a610ff0c28e","tid":356402,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:52:30.0